Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.88,0:24:19.93,Main01,YAMAZAKI,0,0,0,,A spy's most dangerous assignment\Nis the undercover investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.39,0:24:22.60,Main01,,0,0,0,,I will do anything in my power to approach\Nthe Unstoppable Kotaro
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.70,0:24:26.36,Main01,,0,0,0,,Katsura and round up the\NAnti-Foreigner Faction.
